Winter Olympics 1992:
   Game Stats: Biathlon
-- Minimum weight of a biathlete's .22 caliber rifle: 7.7
pounds.
   -- Percentage of pre-Albertville gold medals in the relay
event won by the Soviet Union: 100
                                                                                                       

